<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="SmartPetGuide Privacy Policy">
  <article class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: May 20, 2026</p>
    <p>SmartPetGuide uses Google Analytics 4 to measure anonymous site usage (pages visited, outbound link clicks). GA4 does not collect names, email addresses, or other personally identifiable information. We do not use cookies, tracking scripts, or analytics beyond this.</p>
    <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>Our site contains affiliate links to Amazon and other retailers. When you click these links and make a purchase, the retailer may place cookies on your device as part of their standard operations. Please refer to each retailer's privacy policy for details.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions: hello@smartpetguide.net</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
